{"tid":1691583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實最大問題係TVB","createTime":"2019-11-03T17:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T06:37:38.000Z","uid":253507,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"411d56e04aa129ed28f41b3e48dd6d47b747fb75","tid":1691583,"uid":253507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:06:34.000Z","msg":"事實係好多老人家屋企都淨係睇TVB<br />\n佢地淨係接收到TVB偏頗到痴線嘅訊息<br />\n有陣時可能佢地真係唔知事情嘅來龍去脈<br />\n其實有冇得做啲咩黎針對TVB嘅新聞？<br />\n可能係每日TVB一有啲咩fake news就cap低<br />\n出<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">快速文宣</span></span>嚟解釋<br />\n<br />\n又或者係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">youtube整個channel</span></span>針對TVB新聞嚟講<br />\n每日就針鳩住TVB <br />\n好多老人家唔識得好多字睇唔到文字新聞<br />\n而youtube佢地就睇同聽得明<br />\n<br />\n唔知咁樣做有冇啲用處？<br />\n因為始終連登仔嘅進化速度快過老人家好多<br />\n有陣時都要佢地一齊有心態上進步先成事<br />\n唔知大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人，湧過去！</span></span>"},{"pid":"02544896f45dd1a6399d4fe6657cb35201f3a033","tid":1691583,"uid":253507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:08:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e82c5ee644bbb9f0bd863751cb2ded12031c17ca","tid":1691583,"uid":175471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"廢除聯合聲明，拒絕共匪統治"},{"pid":"61eec9d67edda702e5459d06cb13529d2ccb2ab6","tid":1691583,"uid":253507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:08:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c20bd601865f67122d68dcbb4521a0bbe620ead2","tid":1691583,"uid":253507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:08:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fad470961a920f5d257446a6a67afc986e3b74b","tid":1691583,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:08:46.000Z","msg":"要搞一場廿萬人反TVB嘅遊行集會，嚇到廣告商瀨屎為止<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691564\" data-auto